  m_Name: Ocean Spirits
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  encounterName: Ocean Spirits
  text: 'As your ship crests a wave and smoothly glides down, a movement to your
    left catches your eye. Four animal heads shaped of water emerge next to your
    ship: a horse, a fish, a shark, and a crab. Their watery mouths move as if to
    speak to you, but nothing comes out. Half a second later, you feel their words
    pierce your brain, speaking directly to your mind. "What offerings do you bring
    us?"'
